instructions: Put the dinner plate on the middle of the table cloth
Place the salad plate within the dinner plate at the center of the table cloth
Place the napkin inside the salad plate, upon the dinner plate on the center of table cloth
Place the wine glass on the upper right corner of the tabe cloth
Place the water glass on the right side of wine glass, close to the right edge of the table cloth
Place the salad fork with its prong pointing up on the lower left corner of the table cloth
Place the dinner fork on the left lower corner of the table cloth with its prong pointing up
Place the dinner knife on the right side of the dinner plate, under the water glass
place te soup spoon on the right side of the dinner knife, under the wine glass
